description: Perfectly positioned across from South Boston’s M Street Beach, this 2017 totally renovated three-bedroom home offers the rare blend of refined interior finishes, two private decks and a GARAGE PARKING space! Step inside to find a bright, open layout flooded with natural light from abundant oversized windows all four sides of the home, with almost 1400 sq on one level. The kitchen is a showstopper—custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, large island and Bosch appliances. The oversized living area leads seamlessly to a private deck, where you can sip your morning coffee with glistening harbor views. All three bedrooms are generously sized, including a luxurious primary suite with gorgeous en suite bath, ample storage and direct access to a second large deck (also accessible off of other bedroom). Central Air. In-Unit Washer/Dryer. Private Basement Storage. Whether you’re upsizing, downsizing, or just ready for waterfront living in a choice location, this is the one to see!
